CRS.src.server.database

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • CRS.src.server.database.Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    Connect between the SQL server and the DBmanager. Simplifies operations for the server, simplify write/read commands for the sql server.
